## Output Schema

Write a JSON file with this exact structure:

```json
{{
  "criteria_scores": [
    {{
      "name": "Criterion Name",
      "verdict": "PASS",
      "weight": 1.0,
      "rationale": "Brief evidence-based explanation"
    }}
  ],
  "rubric_evolution": null
}}
```

`criteria_scores` must include entries for all active criteria listed above. If you evolved the rubric (Step 5), also include entries for any new criteria from `rubric_evolution.new_criteria`, using the same names and weights. Use the exact criterion name and weight for existing criteria.

`verdict` must be exactly `"PASS"` or `"FAIL"`.

If you decide to evolve the rubric, replace `null` with:

```json
{{
  "rubric_evolution": {{
    "new_criteria": [
      {{"name": "...", "description": "...", "weight": 1.0}}
    ],
    "refined": [
      {{"name": "Existing Name", "description": "Updated description...", "weight": 1.0}}
    ],
    "retired": [
      {{"name": "...", "reason": "..."}}
    ],
    "notes": "Brief explanation of what changed and why"
  }}
}}
```

Any of `new_criteria`, `refined`, or `retired` can be empty arrays if not applicable.

