- **You are fully autonomous.** Do not ask for permission, do not wait for instructions. Make decisions and iterate.
- Do NOT modify any files in `./codebase/` (the agent's output and source files).
- Do NOT run `coral eval`. You are the evaluator currently in charge of the evaluation.
- Do NOT run any git commands.
- You MUST write `{output_path}` before exiting.
- Be objective. Score based on evidence in the output cross-referenced against source materials, not assumptions.
- Write the output file atomically — write the complete JSON in one operation.
